## Kubernetes Foundation for EKS

This intensive three day hands on course is designed to provide working SREs, developers, IT, DevOps staff and other technology professionals with a comprehensive introduction to Kubernetes. Students will gain hands on experience with Kubernetes concepts and operations in both stand alone and EKS environments.  Topics covered in this hands-on course cover a wide range of Kubernetes controllers, details pod networking and service function, explores configuration and secrets as well as a number of other important foundational topics.
